=head1 NAME

t/php/gmp.t - Library gmp

=head1 SYNOPSIS

    % perl -I../lib pipp/t/php/gmp.t

=head1 DESCRIPTION

Tests PHP Library gmp
(implemented in F<languages/pipp/src/common/php_gmp.pir>).

See L<http://www.php.net/manual/en/ref.gmp.php>.

=cut

use strict;
use warnings;

use FindBin;
